1. Deploy the app

    1.1. heroku login
    1.2. heroku create planet-service
    1.3. git init
    1.4. heroku git:remote -a planet-service
    1.5. git push heroku master
    1.6. heroku open

2. Monitor the app

    2.1. heroku logs 
    2.2. heroku logs --tail 
    2.3. heroku logs --tail -n 10 
    2.4. Take a look at dashboard
